org.megatome.frame2.front
Class SoapRequestProcessor

java.lang.Object
  org.megatome.frame2.front.SoapRequestProcessor
All Implemented Interfaces:
RequestProcessor
public class SoapRequestProcessor
extends Object

A request models the execution of a SOAP request through the Event and the EventHandlers. It is a primary delegate of RequestProcessor, and brings together the data and logic necessary for processing the request.
